    "client_msg_id": "90e051fb-3da2-4957-9e78-55919c9905b1",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I'd turn Agawu's argument on its head really - I think it's true that there are major, under-acknowledged pitfalls in using notation for analysis.. But these turn out to be massive wins in using notation for synthesis, i.e. composition and especially improvisation",
